  "summaries": [
    {
      "id": 12296,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "The /go/admin/restful/configuration/file/POST/xml path is vulnerable to Cross-Site Request Forgery that can result in an unauthorized user adding to the server cruise-config.xml and gaining complete control of the server. Successful exploitation is made difficult by the need for the admin to be served malicious HTML and for the attacker to have a copy of historical config, such as the nearly-empty empty placeholder file that gets initially generated upon install.\n\n",
